ORDERED Autoists Head Crushed as Car Crashes Upsets AMBLING JtVEPORTER Setting a Precedent Doris Baker was married this week to George Robertson Last month another girl who lived at the same place where Doris stayed before the marriage also entered the state of wedded bliss RR can not help wondering if the fact that both girls lived a the Ernest Lovesee home had anything to do with it 1 o Year After Year The old buggy Oliver Wendell Holmes wrote so much poetry about had nothing on the Christmas tree holder loaned to the Safeway store here by Charles Free jr If you think a Christmas tree holder is just a couple of crossed boards or a wire gadget of some kind youd better revise your opinion This one was brought to this country by Frees grandmother 75 years ago and has operated just about every year since then without re pairs of any kind Its a beautiful silvered revolving gadget that keeps the tree turning anl somewhere in side there is a music box that rings out merrily with Silent Night and"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2025-09-02T13:59:44.364Z", "group": ["ndnp/curiv", "university-of-california-riverside-riverside-ca-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn92070146/1937-12-22/ed-1/?sp=1", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:curiv:batch_curiv_roseheath_ver01:data:sn92070146:00414188849:1937122201:0276/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=463&w=366", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:curiv:batch_curiv_roseheath_ver01:data:sn92070146:00414188849:1937122201:0276/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=927&w=732", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/curiv/batch_curiv_roseheath_ver01/data/sn92070146/00414188849/1937122201/0276.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 1, "language": ["english"], "location": ["san diego county", "el centro", "california", "imperial county", "imperial", "united states"], "location_city": ["el centro"], "location_country": [